shows.plot_overview: A devoted fan quits her stable job to pursue her dreams and finally marries her rockstar crush, Ouji Kazuhiro. But on their wedding day, she learns their marriage comes with one unexpected condition—a sexless arrangement.

shows.title: Hito wa Mitame Janai to Omotteta
shows.plot_overview: A baseball-obsessed man who’s always relied on his personality is forced into the world of fashion, discovering that style might matter more than he ever thought.

The surprise meeting, however, did not last long when Imar was shot during a fight with the head of the drug dealer. Before taking his last breath, Imar handed over his authorization card to the Emir and asked the Emir to fulfill one promise: protect his family. shows.title: Shinyuu no “Dousei Shite” ni “Un” te Iu Made
shows.plot_overview: College roommates and lifelong friends reunite, forcing them to choose between friendship and love.

shows.title: こちら予備自衛英雄補?!
shows.plot_overview: Seven unemployed individuals with uniquely quirky superpowers are secretly gathered by the Ministry of Defense in a locked room to save the world, transforming their personal complexes into Earth's salvation.

shows.title: A Homeless Billionaire Husband for Christmas
顔のない患者-救うか、裁くか-
shows.plot_overview: A surgeon is forced to choose between saving his kidnapped wife and killing an anonymous, faceless patient who might be a dangerous fugitive.

shows.title: The Celebrity Apprentice
shows.plot_overview: Boardrooms and bust-ups in Britain's toughest job interview. Who's all talk and who can deliver?

shows.title: Amanda & Alan's Greek Job
shows.plot_overview: Besties Amanda Holden and Alan Carr take on a big fat Greek renovation on the idyllic Ionian island of Corfu. It’s tearing down walls by day and smashing plates by night.

shows.title: Black and Jewish America: An Interwoven History
shows.plot_overview: Four-part docuseries that explores the complex relationship between Black Americans and Jewish Americans - forged in shared struggle, tested by division, and representing a uniquely American experience.

shows.title: Le meilleur pâtissier : Qui sera plus fort que le grimoire de Mercotte ?
Land of Sin
shows.plot_overview: When teenager Silas is found dead at a farmhouse on the Bjäre peninsula – the perpetually angry, odd but highly intelligent investigator Dani (Krista Kosonen) is teamed up with newly graduated police colleague Malik (Mohammed Nour Oklah) to investigate the case. shows.title: France's Dumbest
shows.plot_overview: Celebrities fight to avoid the title "France's Dumbest". The participants are tested on knowledge that everyone should have, and in each episode the smartest gets to go home. This is the competition no one wants to win!

shows.title: Uso ga Uso de Uso wa Uso da
shows.plot_overview: Haunted by lies and unable to trust anyone, Omori Mitsuko faces a Christmas Eve that turns a struggling izakaya into the center of unexpected chaos.

shows.title: Professional
shows.plot_overview: Haunted by a case he couldn’t solve, ex-detective Amane Ren now hunts the truth as an insurance investigator with unyielding resolve.

shows.title: Konkatsu Battlefield 37
shows.plot_overview: Two 37-year-old single women with completely opposite views on marriage, navigating the chaotic “marriage-hunting battlefield” where their ideals, reality, and pride collide in hilarious ways.

shows.title: 令和に官能小説作ってます
Tsui no Hito
shows.plot_overview: Sosuke Shie, a former detective turned funeral director, and Kotaro Soyogi, an overworked elite employee who’s lost touch with himself. After the sudden death of Soyogi’s mother, their paths cross, and together they confront mortality in their own honest and unconventional ways.

shows.title: Fuyu no Nankasa, Haru no Nankane
shows.plot_overview: Ayana Tsuchida, a 27-year-old novelist working on her third book, has a boyfriend but struggles to fully commit due to painful past relationships. After an unexpected incident, she resolves to take her current relationship seriously, reflecting on her past and searching for what love truly means.

shows.title: Kyou mo Curry desu ka?
shows.plot_overview: Two friends bond over their shared love of curry, exploring renowned restaurants one flavorful bowl at a time.

shows.title: AKIBA LOST
shows.plot_overview: Thirteen years after six girls mysteriously vanished in Akihabara, a live-action game recreating the case blurs into reality when six new women are cast, raising the question of whether AKIBA LOST can ever be completed.

shows.title: Gõ Cửa Nhà Mỹ Nam
shows.plot_overview: The first interactive series in Vietnam.  72 hours with the Rookies from Show It All Vietnam.

shows.title: All We Ever Wanted
shows.plot_overview: A soapy and scandalous drama that uncovers the secrets and class struggles of a wealthy suburb; where a torrid love affair between a ‘have’ Mom and ‘have-not’ single Dad threatens to expose the sins and lies of all of those around them.

shows.title: 通古今后，我养成了未来奸相
shows.plot_overview: Modern-day student Su Jin discovers that a mysterious ancient scroll links her to the past, allowing her to exchange items with Shen Yubai, a frail young noble living in the long-lost Dayue Dynasty. When Su Jin learns the dynasty was destroyed by a future treacherous prime minister, she asks Shen Yubai to help stop the coming disaster—unaware that he may be the very man fated to change history.

shows.title: 地府打工人不想996
shows.plot_overview: Modern office worker Sitang Yu dies and unexpectedly becomes the new Meng Po, tasked with brewing soul-altering soup in the underworld. When her soup accidentally releases four notorious demons, she teams up with King Yan, Jiang Ziwen, to capture them.

shows.title: The Screener
shows.plot_overview: Wary of sending out digital links, an independent filmmaker presents her latest film to a talent agency in their private screening room. When it inevitably leaks, a frantic cover-up begins, until the district attorney decides to prosecute the agency as a white-collar crime syndicate. As the office builds its case, everyone involved becomes a witness… or a potential defendant.

shows.title: Dog Park
shows.plot_overview: Roland, a misanthropic man reluctantly adopted by a quirky dog owner community. Together, they support each other through personal struggles, discovering the value of connection, love, and mutual care amidst their challenges.

shows.title: The Exiled
shows.plot_overview: The sudden death of a small-town gang leader triggers a ruthless power struggle for internal supremacy between his widow, his second-in-command, and emerging new forces.

shows.title: Beat Runners
shows.plot_overview: A Tokusatsu Next Generation project.

shows.title: Idol I
shows.plot_overview: A virtuous star lawyer and devoted fan, defends her favorite idol after he is accused of murder.

shows.title: MuTeLuv: Hello, Is This Luck?
shows.plot_overview: Sixth-year medical student Na is full of talent but no luck. She's always thought that with effort comes success, but events in her life have led her to the suspicion recently that, really, it all comes down to fortune. Most significantly, Na has fallen for Nine, a handsome and intelligent senior beyond her reach. In order to force a change of fortune, Na decides to switch to a lucky phone number. It's then that she meets Leemai and soon she's much more than noticed by her crush.

shows.title: Shaolin heroes
shows.plot_overview: Seven well-known Swedish men travel to South Korea to train as Shaolin monks. Over twelve days they undergo intense physical training and inner-journey work at a temple — designed to challenge them mentally and physically and help them confront personal demons. There are no eliminations or staged “intrigues”; the goal is the internal transformation each participant goes through.

shows.title: Canada Shore
shows.plot_overview: Canadians may have a reputation for being polite, but they can be just as feisty, loud, dramatic, and unapologetic as anyone else. Follows the wildest, most outrageous young Canadians who party with their future chosen family this summer.

shows.title: マトリと狂犬
shows.plot_overview: A drug dealer is forced to become a double agent for rival law enforcement agencies following a murder case.

shows.title: Her Radiance
shows.plot_overview: To uncover the truth behind her sister’s disappearance, medical student Jiang Yuanyue assumes a new identity and infiltrates the influential Zeng family as a maid. Her search leads to the discovery of her sister’s body and exposes the patriarch’s murderous secrets, forcing her and the second young master to confront the family’s darkest truths.

shows.title: The Imposter
shows.plot_overview: A beachfront hotel sparks family conflict when Helen won't sell, despite her children's wishes. The arrival of Amanda, claiming to be Helen's long-lost daughter, adds complexity. As the hotel's fate hangs, deception leads to murder.

shows.title: Kateikyoshi no Kishi Knight desu
shows.plot_overview: A tough yankee gets stuck with a prim tutor to fix his grades, but between the bickering and lessons, he’s shocked to find himself falling for him.

shows.title: The CEO Club
shows.plot_overview: Dive deep into the world of seven trailblazing female CEOs (Serena Williams, Thalia, Dee Ocleppo Hilfiger, Loren Ridinger, Winnie Harlow, Hannah Bronfman, and Isabela Rangel Grutman) as they navigate the triumphs and challenges of both their professional and personal lives. Redefining what it means to lead in today's world, these women enter the next phase of their careers with confidence and clarity forged by life experiences.
